Key.English: This mission does not support JIP. Be punctual next time!
Key.Spanish: Esta misión no soporta JIP. ¡Se puntual la próxima vez!

Key.English: Press F11 to teleport to your squad or any other friendly unit. You have 5 minutes.
Key.Spanish: Presiona F11 para teletransportarte a tu escuadra o otra unidad aliada. Tienes 5 minutos.

Key.English: 5 minutes have passed. You cannot teleport to your squad anymore.
Key.Spanish: Han pasado 5 minutos. Ya no puedes teletransportarte a tu escuadra.
